author: The Virginian-Pilot
title: Men's soccer | Kemp's goal gives Marlins ODAC win
text:
VIRGINIA BEACH Josh Kemp's goal Wednesday proved to be the game-winner as Virginia Wesleyan defeated Hampden-Sydney 1-0 in an ODAC men's game.
Kemp's goal came at 39:39 off a pass from Brandon Rogers.
The Marlins (6-5-2, 3-3-2) play at Roanoke on Saturday.
